short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Restores search functionality to the topbar of the PrimeVue v3 website. Get to your desired documentation page directly.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
After PrimeVue released v4 of its component library, it removed component search functionality from the topbar of it's v3 documentation site.

PrimeVue v3 Search restores that functionality, providing users a simple autocomplete-style input that will redirect them straight to the documentation page of their choice, eliminating the need to toggle the menu and parse the long list of components manually.
